奉仕
ほうし<sup>３</sup>【奉仕】 ﾛｰﾏ(hōshi)
1 〔献身的に働くこと〕 service.
〜する serve; render service(s) 《to…》.
▲地域社会に奉仕する　serve the local community
・神に奉仕する　serve God.
▲奉仕の精神　a spirit of service.
2 〔商品などを安く提供すること〕 offer goods at a reduced price.
〜する offer at a (greatly) reduced price; 〔無料で〕 give one's services free.
▲ここにある商品はすべて半額にてご奉仕いたしております.　All the goods here are being given away at half price!
◨勤労奉仕　labor service.
社会奉仕　community [voluntary social] service.
◧奉仕価格
▲奉仕価格で　《sell》 at a sacrifice; 《offer》 at a ⌐reduced [bargain] price
・特別奉仕価格　a specially reduced price; a special-sacrifice price.
奉仕活動　volunteer work.
奉仕事業　volunteer work.
奉仕者　one who ⌐serves [offers his services to] 《the community》; a volunteer.
奉仕団　a volunteer group.
奉仕品　a bargain.
